ActPest Control Products Act
PrecisPEST CONTROL PRODUCTS INCIDENT REPORTING REGULATIONS which require applicants and anyone in whose name a pest control product has been registered to report any adverse effects involving their product that occur in Canada and the United States, or that are generated through studies conducted anywhere in the world, to the Pest Control Management Agency.
